{"tid":409903,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"我諗到點樣用AI 加 VR 去創造完美世界","createTime":"2017-09-22T12:31:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T07:28:19.000Z","uid":54581,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4869817f5d287c0d21b22bf5489360047aecfb2a","tid":409903,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:31:55.000Z","msg":"首先，我相信要做到SAO咁既VR 加 可以從事任何行業既AI 其實係可行既<br />\n<br />\n問題係要100年，200年定更多既時間。<br />\n<br />\n當做到之後，全世界訓係個倉到 體驗虛擬人生<br />\n<br />\n可以學野+旅行+做任何野。<br />\n<br />\nEven將時間較快，係虛擬世界體驗10年等於現實過左1年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所有世界維持，人類身體營養補充 做手術靠AI<br />\n<br />\n為免地球人口急劇上升，每人只限生最多一個小孩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得技術上可唔可行"},{"pid":"469633899756828ab9b76b9568b77315146916a8","tid":409903,"uid":14439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:37:37.000Z","msg":"可行"},{"pid":"88ef1e17660e8ca23322997ab0f42db8b319e1fe","tid":409903,"uid":109598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:38:43.000Z","msg":"咪撚on9"},{"pid":"6d7997b500662db4fff7e8aa448ab07cf374e802","tid":409903,"uid":531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:40:00.000Z","msg":"Even將時間較快，係虛擬世界體驗10年等於現實過左1年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fae75b3277ef5de6082665c43a8a86dfcf4c18b","tid":409903,"uid":69221,"like":1,"dislike